mapper.select:
select ndp_subject.subject_id,ndp_subject.subject_name,ndp_category.category_name,left(ndp_subject.create_time,10) create_time,ndp_subject.subject_desc from ndp_subject,ndp_category where ndp_subject.category_id = ndp_category.category_id
and ndp_subject.category_id = #{category_id}
order by ndp_subject.create_time desc limit 5
